### AidFlow API — Programs endpoints
# REST Client extension: click 'Send Request' above each block

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000/api/v1
@token = REPLACE_WITH_JWT_TOKEN

### List programs (501 in Sprint 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/programs
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get program by ID (501 in Sprint 1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/programs/PROGRAM_ID
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create program (501 in Sprint 1)
POST {{baseUrl}}/programs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Food Aid 2026",
  "description": "Emergency food distribution program",
  "targetAmount": 100000,
  "currency": "USD"
}

### Update program (501 in Sprint 1)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/programs/PROGRAM_ID
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Food Aid 2026 — Updated"
}

### Delete program (501 in Sprint 1)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/programs/PROGRAM_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
